verbose_text: The aim of the present study was to provide more comprehensive transcriptome profiling of macrophages to inflammatory stimulation, was enhanced through the use of RNA-seq technology to examine IFN-gamma-mediated TLR4 cross regulation, IL-4 / IL-13-primed M2 macrophage polarization and differences between RAW264.7 macrophages and BMDMs.
